snippet.title: Cubey - Private Beta Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the beta today at https://www.unboxedgames.xyz/games/cubey/private-beta-program

What's Cubey?

Cubey is an Indie 3D Strategy type game where you try your best to avoid obstacles, if you even slightly touch them you start back from the beginning of the level.
